          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mt-4">Negotiating $4-6/hr above the median is a fast way to move from a 95 SIRS score to 105+ without changing anything else about your profile. Many BC tech employers are willing to adjust salary slightly when they understand it directly affects the candidate's PR pathway.</p>
